node.text:
🍰 Strawberry Shortcake 🍰
.
Baked this #strawberryshortcake for my son's birthday.
.
Flies really flies, in a blink of the eye, you are already 18 years old, approaching adulthood soon. Mummy wishes the best for you and I love you forever ❤❤❤
@piggylovesdesserts your birthday today? Happy birthday! My son's birthday was yesterday
@serenefoodology Thank you!  A belated happy birthday to him then!
Oh is his birthday today?  Same as mine?  Happy birthday to him too! 😂
Pretty and yummy cake 🎂 Happy Birthday to your son
@goofytwocooks thank you, happy belated birthday to you!
Happy Birthday to your son and nice cake 😍
Happy Birthday to your son! And your cake looks yummy 😍
Birthday blessings to your young man! Blessed 18th!
@belandbray thank you, Karen! Hahaha... can consider 😆😆
Happy birthday to him! Do you have delivery order too? 😄
@belbuttons thank you! Wow.. your's even older! 😄😄
Happy Birthday to your young man! May all his heart’s desires be fulfilled! Yes too quickly they grow up. Mine celebrating 23 next week 😱 ...
Pretty cake! Happy birthday to your prince. 🎂
Looks really good!!! Happy birthday to him😊
Happy birthday to your prince 😍 You look so young.
Happy birthday to your son, have a blessed and joyful one! ❤️
Wishing you son blesses birtbday! Hope u guys had a memorable celebration.😍
May you son have a blessed birthday with these beautiful sunshine strawberry cake.🎉🎂
